Davenport.K283BV:
K283BV (104.5) is an alternative radio station serving the quad cities that blends new music with alternative such as Mumford & sons, Twenty One Pilots etc.


== History ==
104.5 debuted at 1:04 PM on August 21, 2015 replacing what was presumed to be a simulcast of WLLR. Jim O'Hara, Iheart Radio Quad Cities SVP Programmer, says the station blends new music with alternative playing Mumford & sons, Twenty One Pilots, Kings of Leon, etc.
